  entryId: day_01_bridge_repaired
  dayNumber: 1
  title: Bridge Repaired
  bodyText: 'The bridge was broken at dawn.

    I found usable timber in Darkwood and repaired the crossing before the day faded.


    Tomorrow, the villagers may not remember who did it.

    The bridge will.'
  illustration: {fileID: 0}
  clueIds: []
  proofText: The bridge remains, even if no one remembers who repaired it.
